<div class="container" style="max-width: 1200px;">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12">
      <div class="pricing-header p-4 pb-md-5 mt-5 mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-3">Postman Toolbox</h1>
        <p class="fs-5 mb-0" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;">
          A suite of tools built by the Postman Solutions Engineering team to streamline API development and governance.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row g-4 mb-5">
    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
      <div class="card h-100">
        <div class="card-header py-4">
          <h4 class="my-0 fw-semibold">Governance Rules Playground</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column text-start p-4">
          <p class="mb-3">Write and test custom Spectral rules against your OpenAPI or AsyncAPI specifications.</p>
          <p class="mb-auto">View JSONPath matches and detailed validation results to ensure your APIs follow governance standards.</p>
          <a class="w-100 mt-4 btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="/governance-playground">
            Open Playground →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
      <div class="card h-100">
        <div class="card-header py-4">
          <h4 class="my-0 fw-semibold">Visual Test Composer</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column text-start p-4">
          <p class="mb-3">Generate Postman test scripts from JSON responses using an intuitive visual interface.</p>
          <p class="mb-auto">Build Chai assertions without writing code—just paste your JSON and configure the tests visually.</p>
          <a class="w-100 mt-4 btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="/test-composer">
            Open Composer →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
      <div class="card h-100">
        <div class="card-header py-4">
          <h4 class="my-0 fw-semibold">Test Reporter</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column text-start p-4">
          <p class="mb-3">Transform Postman Collection Runner results into beautiful, shareable visual reports.</p>
          <p class="mb-auto">Upload your exported JSON to see charts, metrics, and detailed test breakdowns.</p>
          <a class="w-100 mt-4 btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="/test-reporter">
            Open Reporter →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row mb-5">
    <div class="col-12 text-center">
      <p class="text-muted small">
        Built with ❤️ by the Postman Solutions Engineering team  |
        <a href="https://github.com/postman-solutions-eng/postman-toolbox" target="_blank" style="color: var(--color-accent);">View on GitHub</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
